Creating images with R

with a little bit of magick

Yunuo Wu

2023/3/11

My meme

This meme depicts my distinct feelings of the beginning of semester and the end of semester.

I used energetic Cheems (the doggy) to show that many students are happy and confident when the new semester is coming. I used tired/sad Cheems to show that students are tired/sad when the final exam is coming. I never see this meme on the internet and it would be fun if I create a meme to depict our students real feelings of study.

My animated GIF

Same as the meme, this gif depicts my changing feelings of whole semester.

I used happy Cheems, unhappy Cheems, sad Cheems, weepy Cheems and tired Cheems to depict my feelings of different stages of the semester. I never see this Gif on the internet and it would be fun if I create a Gif to depict students real feelings of study.
